body:
I kind of dig the new Mastery system, and the grades at the end of matches are interesting. Could we perhaps have a page explaining why we received the grade we did, maybe as a point of reference to what we could improve upon for that champion/role?

Perhaps break the grade down as a percentage based on wards, cs, KDA and so forth, based upon how the grade is derived from similar champs played in that role. Probably couldn&#039;t fit it on the end of match summary page, but you could add a tab to the match history site. I think it might add some insight into Riot&#039;s grading scale, and maybe encourage a few people to focus on areas to improve. 

And, you know, ward more. {{item:3361}}
